articles.title: George Santos speaks out on possibly facing jail time | CNN Politics
articles.description: Former New York Republican Rep. George Santos is talking with federal prosecutors about a possible plea deal, according to court records. In an interview with CBS New York, Santos addressed the possibility. CNN’s Brynn Gingras has the details.
